---
const imgLogo = "/assets/figma/LogoBuilt.svg"
---
<section class="flex w-full justify-center flex-col items-center gap-4 lg:gap-6 px-6 py-8">

  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 lg:gap-4 border-2 border-black px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full">
    <div class="border-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-black bg-red-500"></div>
    <span class="text-xs lg:text-base font-bold">GDG Sucre presenta</span>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:py-16">
    <img alt="" class="block max-w-none size-full w-full object-contain" src={imgLogo} />
  </div>

  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 lg:gap-4 border-2 border-black px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full">
    <span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold">Sucre 2026</span>
  </div>

  <p class="text-base lg:text-xl">Dos días para aprender, construir y conectar con la comunidad que está armando el futuro con IA en Bolivia.</p>

      <!-- Actions -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[15px] items-start not-italic relative shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap" style="height: 156px; width: 420px;">
      <a href="#registro" class="bg-[#1e1e1e] border-2 border-[#1e1e1e] flex gap-[10px] items-center justify-center overflow-clip px-[22px] py-[20px] rounded-[999px] shrink-0 text-white w-full hover:bg-[#333] transition-colors" style="height: 71px;">
        <p class="font-['Google_Sans',sans-serif] font-bold text-[25px] text-center leading-normal">Quiero mi lugar</p>
        <p class="font-['Inter',sans-serif] font-bold text-[20px] leading-normal">→</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#agenda" class="bg-white border-2 border-[#1e1e1e] flex gap-[10px] items-center justify-center overflow-clip px-[22px] py-[20px] rounded-[999px] shrink-0 text-[#1e1e1e] w-full hover:bg-[#f0f0f0] transition-colors">
        <p class="font-['Google_Sans',sans-serif] font-bold text-[25px] text-center leading-normal">Ver agenda</p>
        <p class="font-['Inter',sans-serif] font-bold text-[20px] leading-normal">→</p>
      </a>
    </div>

</section>